    <briefdescription>
<para>Visitor that checks if an expression tree contains an imaginary unit. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The imaginary unit in LMCAS is represented as sqrt(-1), i.e., a <ref refid="d7/d06/classFunctionNode" kindref="compound">FunctionNode</ref> with type Sqrt and a single argument that is a <ref refid="dc/dea/classNumberNode" kindref="compound">NumberNode</ref> with value -1. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
